item.title: CVE-2023-45038|2024-09-06T17:44:36.623Z -- qnap%20systems%20inc. -- music%20station
item.description:
An improper authentication vulnerability has been reported to affect Music Station. If exploited, the vulnerability could allow users to compromise the security of the system via a network.
We have already fixed the vulnerability in the following version: Music Station 5.4.0 and later
